Christmas Wrap

On the Coq, Al gets the charred remains of a grocery truck off the road, using an excavator to tear up the wreck and load it on a lowboy trailer. In Alberta, Collin rights a 5 ton mail truck that rolled tearing the roof open. After a recovery team unloads the mail Collin gets the 5 ton out of the ditch. In the Frasier Valley, Nick has inches to pull a brand new box truck out of the ditch that is resting very close to a power pole
